statements: SELECT * FROM vendor_risk_assessment;
SELECT vendor_name, reputation FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE financial_stability = 'Stable';
SELECT id, vendor_name, service_quality FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE reputation = 'Good' ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT vendor_name, service_quality FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE financial_stability IN ('Stable', 'Unstable') ORDER BY vendor_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE financial_stability = 'Unstable' AND service_quality = 'Poor';
SELECT * FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE financial_stability = 'Stable' AND service_quality = 'High';
SELECT vendor_name, reputation FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE reputation LIKE '%Positive%' ORDER BY vendor_name DESC;
SELECT id, vendor_name, financial_stability FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE financial_stability = 'Unstable' ORDER BY id LIMIT 5;
SELECT vendor_name, service_quality FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE service_quality = 'Medium' OR service_quality = 'Low' LIMIT 10 OFFSET 5;
SELECT * FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE reputation NOT LIKE '%Negative%' AND financial_stability = 'Stable' ORDER BY reputation ASC, vendor_name ASC;
SELECT vendor_id, financial_stability_rating, reputation_rating, service_quality_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments;
SELECT * FROM vendor_details WHERE vendor_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT vendor_name, registration_date FROM vendor_details WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT vendor_name, contact_email FROM vendor_details ORDER BY vendor_name ASC;
SELECT vendor_id, financial_stability_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments WHERE financial_stability_rating > 8.0;
SELECT vendor_id, financial_stability_rating, reputation_rating, service_quality_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments ORDER BY vendor_id DESC;
SELECT vendor_id, vendor_name, registration_date, contact_email FROM vendor_details WHERE registration_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT vendor_id, financial_stability_rating, reputation_rating, service_quality_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments WHERE financial_stability_rating > 8 AND reputation_rating < 5;
SELECT vendor_id, vendor_name, registration_date, contact_email FROM vendor_details ORDER BY registration_date ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT vendor_id, vendor_name, registration_date, contact_email FROM vendor_details WHERE vendor_name LIKE '%tech%' ORDER BY vendor_id DESC;
SELECT vendor_id, vendor_name, financial_stability_rating, reputation_rating, service_quality_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments;
SELECT vendor_name, financial_stability_rating, reputation_rating, service_quality_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments ORDER BY vendor_name DESC;
SELECT vendor_name, financial_stability_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments WHERE financial_stability_rating > 80;
SELECT vendor_name, service_quality_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments WHERE service_quality_rating < 70;
SELECT * FROM service_quality_feedback WHERE feedback_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM vendor_risk_assessments WHERE financial_stability_rating > 3 ORDER BY vendor_name ASC;
SELECT vendor_name, reputation_rating, service_quality_rating FROM vendor_risk_assessments WHERE vendor_id = 5;
SELECT vendor_name, AVG(financial_stability_rating) AS avg_financial_stability FROM vendor_risk_assessments GROUP BY vendor_name HAVING avg_financial_stability > 4;
SELECT vendor_name, feedback_text FROM vendor_risk_assessments INNER JOIN service_quality_feedback ON vendor_risk_assessments.vendor_id = service_quality_feedback.vendor_id;
SELECT vendor_name, MAX(score_value) AS max_score FROM vendor_risk_assessments INNER JOIN financial_stability_scores ON vendor_risk_assessments.vendor_id = financial_stability_scores.vendor_id;
SELECT * FROM vendors;
SELECT vendor_name, financial_stability FROM vendors WHERE service_quality > 4.5;
SELECT vendor_name, reputation, service_quality FROM vendors ORDER BY vendor_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM financial_scores WHERE score >= 80;
SELECT assessment_date, assessed_by, vendor_id FROM assessments WHERE assessment_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM vendors ORDER BY financial_stability DESC, reputation ASC;
SELECT vendor_name, service_quality FROM vendors WHERE service_quality > 4;
SELECT assessments.assessment_id, assessments.vendor_id, vendors.vendor_name FROM assessments JOIN vendors ON assessments.vendor_id = vendors.id;
SELECT vendor_name, financial_stability, (financial_stability * service_quality) AS stability_quality_score FROM vendors;
SELECT vendor_name, fiscal_year, score FROM financial_scores WHERE fiscal_year = 2021 ORDER BY score DESC;
SELECT * FROM vendor_risk_assessment ORDER BY vendor_name DESC;
SELECT vendor_name, financial_stability_score, reputation_score FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE financial_stability_score > 80;
SELECT vendor_name, service_quality_score FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE service_quality_score < 70 ORDER BY service_quality_score ASC;

SELECT vendor_risk_assessment.vendor_name, reputation_review.review_date, reputation_review.reviewer_name FROM vendor_risk_assessment JOIN reputation_review ON vendor_risk_assessment.id = reputation_review.vendor_id;
SELECT vendor_name, financial_stability_score, debt_ratio FROM vendor_risk_assessment JOIN financial_stability_report ON vendor_risk_assessment.id = financial_stability_report.vendor_id;
SELECT * FROM vendor_risk_assessment ORDER BY vendor_name DESC;
SELECT vendor_name, financial_stability_score, reputation_score FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE financial_stability_score > 80 AND reputation_score > 70;
SELECT vendor_name, service_quality_score FROM vendor_risk_assessment WHERE service_quality_score < 50 ORDER BY service_quality_score ASC;
SELECT vendor_name, stability_rating, annual_revenue FROM vendor_risk_assessment JOIN financial_stability_report ON vendor_risk_assessment.id = financial_stability_report.vendor_id;
SELECT vendor_name, review_description FROM vendor_risk_assessment JOIN reputation_review ON vendor_risk_assessment.id = reputation_review.vendor_id WHERE review_date > '2022-01-01';
